{
  "stem": "24259.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct, correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certain things, I remember very vividly, and-- and certain areas [? way ?] I-- where I played with my cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember where the horses stood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to jump off the roof of that little shed where they were kept.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember specifically that we had some pigs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- this is later on, maybe a few weeks later, the pigs-- one of the pigs gave birth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember there was a whole big to-do about that and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father, of course, kind of scouted around the area with the Russians and, with their help, was able to go back to the-- to the farm.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- We-- we didn't stay very long, perhaps several months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my father, I guess through conversations with others, found that it was not very safe for us to-- to stay in that area.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was able to procure papers as us being Polish citizens, to move further into Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we packed up, and-- and-- so to speak, and moved to another part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That part of Poland became part of Russia, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that-- he felt that would be safer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, my father had visions of eventually emigrating to Israel, which was then Palestine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was the original intent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But as Polish citizens, we were able to move to another part of Poland, to a city called Bytom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I believe it's spelled B-Y-T-O-M.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe several hundred kilometers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was a large city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- we were just there a short period of time.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
